title: RAW Rolling Papers
description: These RAW rolling papers are pure and 100% natural. Raw rolling papers contain a hybrid blend of unbleached fibers; RAW showcases this by showing the user the paper's natural color. RAW is so thin that you can see right through it, yet durable enough to enjoy a good smoke. Each paper contains RAW's uniquely designed watermark that helps prevent runs and maintains the smooth, even burning characteristics that RAW is famous for.
